ivardefs.name: activeOnly
ivardefs.desc: Controls whether inactive concepts are included or excluded in value set expansions.

ivardefs.name: contact_
ivardefs.desc: Contact details to assist a user in finding and communicating with the publisher.

ivardefs.name: date
ivardefs.desc: The date  (and optionally time) when the expansion profile was published. The date must change if and when the business version changes and it must change if the status code changes. In addition, it should change when the substantive content of the expans

ivardefs.name: description
ivardefs.desc: A free text natural language description of the expansion profile from a consumer's perspective.

ivardefs.name: designation
ivardefs.desc: A set of criteria that provide the constraints imposed on the value set expansion by including or excluding designations.

ivardefs.name: displayLanguage
ivardefs.desc: Specifies the language to be used for description in the expansions i.e. the language to be used for ValueSet.expansion.contains.display.

ivardefs.name: excludedSystem
ivardefs.desc: Code system, or a particular version of a code system to be excluded from value set expansions.

ivardefs.name: excludeNested
ivardefs.desc: Controls whether or not the value set expansion nests codes or not (i.e. ValueSet.expansion.contains.contains).

ivardefs.name: excludeNotForUI
ivardefs.desc: Controls whether or not the value set expansion includes codes which cannot be displayed in user interfaces.

ivardefs.name: excludePostCoordinated
ivardefs.desc: Controls whether or not the value set expansion includes post coordinated codes.

ivardefs.name: experimental
ivardefs.desc: A boolean value to indicate that this expansion profile is authored for testing purposes (or education/evaluation/marketing), and is not intended to be used for genuine usage.

ivardefs.name: fixedVersion_
ivardefs.desc: Fix use of a particular code system to a particular version.

ivardefs.name: identifier
ivardefs.desc: A formal identifier that is used to identify this expansion profile when it is represented in other formats, or referenced in a specification, model, design or an instance.

ivardefs.name: includeDefinition
ivardefs.desc: Controls whether the value set definition is included or excluded in value set expansions.

ivardefs.name: includeDesignations
ivardefs.desc: Controls whether concept designations are to be included or excluded in value set expansions.

ivardefs.name: jurisdiction_
ivardefs.desc: A legal or geographic region in which the expansion profile is intended to be used.

ivardefs.name: limitedExpansion
ivardefs.desc: If the value set being expanded is incomplete (because it is too big to expand), return a limited expansion (a subset) with an indicator that expansion is incomplete, using the extension [http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/valueset-toocostly](extensi

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: A natural language name identifying the expansion profile. This name should be usable as an identifier for the module by machine processing applications such as code generation.

ivardefs.name: publisher
ivardefs.desc: The name of the individual or organization that published the expansion profile.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: The status of this expansion profile. Enables tracking the life-cycle of the content.

ivardefs.name: url
ivardefs.desc: An absolute URI that is used to identify this expansion profile when it is referenced in a specification, model, design or an instance. This SHALL be a URL, SHOULD be globally unique, and SHOULD be an address at which this expansion profile is (or will be

ivardefs.name: useContext_
ivardefs.desc: The content was developed with a focus and intent of supporting the contexts that are listed. These terms may be used to assist with indexing and searching for appropriate expansion profile instances.

ivardefs.name: version
ivardefs.desc: The identifier that is used to identify this version of the expansion profile when it is referenced in a specification, model, design or instance. This is an arbitrary value managed by the expansion profile author and is not expected to be globally unique
